      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "P+"                 to   s-ope                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Sistema applicativo                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      i-ide-sap            to   s-sap                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Area gestionale                                 *
