      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "pgm/gep/prg/obj/pgep8400"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat                                            .
           cancel    s-pat                                            .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Segnale di interruzione interrogazione      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-qry-flg-int      .
       qry-trt-fun-999.
           exit.

